title: Grandia II OSTs [mp3]
description:
Grandia II is a Sega Dreamcast game with music composed by Noriyuki Iwadare. The OST was released on two discs, ~Deus~ and ~Povo~, with another disc, ~Melodia~, being packed with the limited edition of the game. This torrent also includes songs from the bonus disc, and represents the highest quality MP3s I could find.

~Deus~ and ~Povo~ were converted to high-quality MP3 from FLAC and songs vary between 260-320kbps. ~Melodia~ is lower quality (120-210kbps), and the bonus disc is all 320kbps.

-

Please continue to share this music for future listeners.
